1
00:00:00,050 --> 00:00:07,587
The instrument is a SAFE bridge — twenty percent discount, no cap, 1.25 times share advantage, rolling close.

2
00:00:07,587 --> 00:00:11,350
Capital funds three discrete catalysts in twelve months.

3
00:00:11,350 --> 00:00:13,687
First, the commercial team build-out.

4
00:00:13,687 --> 00:00:22,562
Second, two AMC master service agreements plus Bio-RAG expansion from eight point six million to fifteen million vectors.

5
00:00:22,562 --> 00:00:27,425
Third, a top-twenty pharma companion-diagnostic co-development deal.

6
00:00:27,425 --> 00:00:29,912
Each catalyst re-rates the platform.

7
00:00:29,912 --> 00:00:39,737
Sixty million today, one hundred ten to one hundred forty after one, one fifty to one eighty after two, three hundred fifty to five hundred after three.

8
00:00:39,737 --> 00:00:46,687
A SAFE today converts against a roughly five-times re-rate, compounded by the discount and share advantage.

